text: Kristine Esebua is an archer from Georgia. She was born on 19 March 1985. Esebua competed at the 2004, 2008, 2012, and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Kristine EsebuaKristine ESEBUA == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Archers from Georgia (country) Category:Olympians for Georgia (country)
